== Amezruy n At Yexlef ==
At Yexlef (Ait Ikhlef) ttaddart id izggan di temnaṭ n Lɛaṛc n At Yeǧǧar, teṭṭef tiɣilt nnig u aqacuc lqarn di tama u Assamar n Tiɣiwant n Buzgan ([[:fr:Bouzeguène|Bouzeguène]]), azal n yiwen u kilumiṭre af teẓgi nu Akfadu, tettwassen s-iɣaṛsiwen d y-imɣan. Taddart n Tizuyin ar tama u Agafa, At Mizart (At Sidi Ḥend Waɛli) uk d Iḥiṭusan ar w Anẓul, taɣiwant n Buzgan ar tama u Amalu,  Imuɣlawen uk Lqelɛa ar tama u Assamar.

Azal n {{unité|1400|imezdaɣ}} (Leḥseb n Ɣuct 2014) amur amuqṛan degssen ttidirren anda niḍan (Taɣiwant n Tizi uzu, Ldzayer, di yal tama n tmurt n Ldzzayer yuk di tmurra lvaṛani am Fṛansa. Sevɛa i derma i ttidirren dina : Imesɛuden (Messaoudene), Iveyxiren (Belkhir), At Ɛli (Kashi ), At Ɛiciwt (Slimani), At Mesɛud (Messaoudi), At Mḥend (Mettouchi), yukk d At Rabaḥ (Rabia). 

At Yexlef ttaddart y uran ismis deg umezruy, aṭṭas id efkka i tagrawla am aṭṭas n tuddrin niḍan n tmurt n Iqbayliyin. Amur n ilmaẓyen id yekkran mgal amnakcam effkan iman-nsen d asfel i tagrawla n 1954-1962 am wid y izwarren ar umennuɣ si zik yakan (1871). Ssuq n Ttlata d yiwen ye-ttilin yal dduṛt d anar n temlilit d menuɣ id yebbin ilmazyen ad kecmen ar FLN. Tddart n At Yexlef txellelṣ-itt aɣlayet ami i tella ar tama n tagrawla, tajmilt i wid yemutten ami ismawen n sen ttewjarden di yemast n taddart. Taddart At Yexlef ttamenzut anda d yella uɣerbaz amenzu n temnaṭṭ n At ɣeǧǧer id s ved Fṛansa, yezgadd azal n 500 lmittrat ɣef taddart assegas n 1898, aṭṭas id yettassan deg yakk tudrin is d yazin.

Lbusṭṭa n Buzgan ar-assa tewwi isem n taddart At Yexlef « poste d’Ait Ikhlef » deg asmi itt tesbeb Fṛansa.

Timetti di taddart teqqim am zman aqbuṛ t bed yef « tajmaɛt » yas akken neǧǧa aṭṭas. Triciti tewḍed assegas n 1982, aman deg lgaz kecman ar y ixxaman, annar iy ḍumman ittewhega s leqdic n ilmezian.

